channel.title: Hacking tunnel 1.0
channel.description:
Basically this application relays packets between a client and a server, and gives you the power to modify them however you please. Its mainly just a library i wrote, but I've included an implementation with a shitty GUI. You have to find a way to spoof the client to connect to localhost. I'm not sure if anyone can find a use for it, but i thought it to be pretty useful so thats why I'm posting it :P
[url=http://files.xnr.be/7477383e0efbca6576f843eb1f52ee01.rar]Download here[/url]
Edit: oh yes, post bugs if you find some
